title: Midway Cafe and Coffee Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This Upper Florida Keys cafe offers veggie choices like tofu wrap, hummus wrap, veggie wrap, portabella mushroom sandwich, and breakfast items with eggs served all day. Meat in some dishes can be substituted with tofu. Serves fair trade coffee. Uses recyclable cups and plates.
